35/* returns 1 if device is one of the nv4x using the 0x4497 object class,
36 * helpful to determine a number of other hardware features
37 */
38static inline int
39nv44_gr_class(struct nvkm_device *device)
40{
41 if ((device->chipset & 0xf0) == 0x60)
42 return 1;
43
44 return !(0x0aaf & (1 << (device->chipset & 0x0f)));
45}
